## Memory — Append to `logs/TEST_SESSION.md`

Create `logs/` if it does not exist. Append one YAML block per run, never overwrite.

```yaml
---
timestamp: "<ISO 8601>"
diff:
  files_changed: []
  lines_added: 0
  lines_removed: 0
scope:
  decision: "diff-only"                 # diff-only | expanded
  reason: null                          # omit if diff-only
  extra_files: []                       # omit if diff-only
coverage_gaps:
  - file: ""
    lines: ""
    description: ""
scenarios_proposed:
  - id: 1
    title: ""
    risk: ""
    selected: false
tests_generated:
  - scenario_id: 1
    file: ""
    test_names: []
test_run:
  status: "skipped"                     # passed | failed | skipped
  failed_tests: []
  error_summary: null
---
```

